"  Garden Tomato Juice","3 pounds very ripe red or yellow tomatoes, coarsely chopped","1 1/4 cups chopped celery with leaves","1/3 cup chopped onion","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground pepper","  Cocktail","1 tablespoon kosher salt","1 tablespoon finely chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","1  lime wedge","1/2  medium tomato, seeded and chopped","1  fresh basil sprig","1/4 cup gin","  Garnishes: cucumber spears, celery ribs, fresh basil sprigs, lime wedges"